query:
SELECT 'Fábio' as tipo, g.id as gestorId, g.userId, u.name
FROM gestores g
INNER JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id
WHERE u.name LIKE '%Fábio%' OR u.name LIKE '%Fabio%'
UNION ALL
SELECT 'Criador Relatórios' as tipo, g.id as gestorId, g.userId, u.name
FROM gestores g
INNER JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id
WHERE g.id IN (SELECT DISTINCT gestorId FROM relatorios_livres);
